#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Chemistry Practitioner"
msgstr "化學實踐者"

#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Chemistry Practitioner"
msgstr "化學實踐者"

#. ~ Profession (male Chemistry Practitioner) description
#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"Whether you were from a working class neighborhood or the halls of high "
"society, people around you had more than a passing interest in various "
"substances. You on the other hand, were far more interested in the science "
"of chemisty than imbibing various spirits and drugs."
msgstr "無論出身工人街區還是上流社會，周遭人們對各類物質的興趣皆不止於淺嘗。而你卻遠比對暢飲烈酒或沉迷藥物更痴迷於化學科學。"

#. ~ Profession (female Chemistry Practitioner) description
#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"Whether you were from a working class neighborhood or the halls of high "
"society, people around you had more than a passing interest in various "
"substances. You on the other hand, were far more interested in the science "
"of chemisty than imbibing various spirits and drugs."
msgstr "無論出身工人街區還是上流社會，周遭人們對各類物質的興趣皆不止於淺嘗。而你卻遠比對暢飲烈酒或沉迷藥物更痴迷於化學科學。"

#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Engineer of Electricity"
msgstr "電氣工程師"

#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Engineer of Electricity"
msgstr "電氣工程師"

#. ~ Profession (male Engineer of Electricity) description
#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"Most people around you were content to enjoy the glow of the new electric "
"streetlamps, but you always yearned for more knowledge about this marvelous "
"spark. After years of hard work, you have finally become well versed in the "
"study of electricity and its myriad concepts."
msgstr "當多數人滿足於欣賞新式電燈街燈的光芒時，你始終渴望更深入理解這奇妙火花。經年努力後，你終於通曉電力及其紛繁概念的研究。"

#. ~ Profession (female Engineer of Electricity) description
#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"Most people around you were content to enjoy the glow of the new electric "
"streetlamps, but you always yearned for more knowledge about this marvelous "
