#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Town Soldier"
msgstr "城鎮士兵"

#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Town Soldier"
msgstr "城鎮士兵"

#. ~ Profession (male Town Soldier) description
#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"Perhaps out of wanderlust or a desire to protect your fellow townsfolk, you "
"decided to enlist in the town's local military. With a few years of "
"experience under your belt, you've become quite an accomplished soldier."
msgstr "或許是出於漫遊之念，抑或守護鎮民之願，你選擇加入本地城鎮軍隊。積累數年經驗後，已成為一名頗具建樹的士兵。"

