msgstr "城鎮守衛"

#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Town Guardswoman"
msgstr "城鎮女守衛"

#. ~ Profession (male Town Guard) description
#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"Perhaps out of wanderlust or a desire to protect your fellow townsfolk, you "
"decided to enlist in the town's local military. With only a few months of "
"training, you don't know much about the art of warfare yet."
msgstr "或許是出於漫遊的渴望，或是保護鎮上同胞的願望，你決定加入當地的城鎮軍隊。僅經過幾個月的訓練，你對戰爭藝術還知之甚少。"

#. ~ Profession (female Town Guardswoman) description
#: .\sp_professions.json
