msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Town Elite"
msgstr "城鎮精英"

#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Town Elite"
msgstr "城鎮精英"

#. ~ Profession (male Town Elite) description
#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"Perhaps out of wanderlust or a desire to protect your fellow townsfolk, you "
"decided to enlist in the town's local military. You are one of the select "
"few deemed skilled enough to use machined plate armor."
msgstr "或許是出於漫遊的渴望，或是保護鎮上同胞的願望，你決定加入當地的城鎮軍隊。你是少數被選中、技藝足以使用機械板甲的人之一。"

