#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Unhinged Scientist"
msgstr "瘋狂科學家"

#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Unhinged Scientist"
msgstr "瘋狂科學家"

#. ~ Profession (male Unhinged Scientist) description
#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"Despite all your talent, despite all your intellect, nobody has EVER "
"respected your genius! Well now, they'll all see, when your machines and "
"weapons of war are unleashed upon polite society."
msgstr "儘管你才華橫溢，儘管你智慧超群，但從未有人尊重過你的天才！好吧，現在他們都會看到的，當你的機器和戰爭武器被釋放到文明社會時。"

