#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Man of Leisure"
msgstr "悠閒紳士"

#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Upper Class Woman"
msgstr "上流社會女性"

#. ~ Profession (male Man of Leisure) description
#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You were born with a silver spoon firmly in your mouth. While the other "
"classes of society labored and toiled, you were fit to rule, and learned the"
" finer aspects of high society."
msgstr "你生來就含著金湯匙。當社會其他階層辛勤勞作時，你生來適合統治，並學習了上流社會的精緻方面。"

#. ~ Profession (female Upper Class Woman) description
#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You were born with a silver spoon firmly in your mouth. While the other "
"classes of society labored and toiled, you were fit to rule, and learned the"
" finer aspects of high society."
msgstr "你生來就含著金湯匙。當社會其他階層辛勤勞作時，你生來適合統治，並學習了上流社會的精緻方面。"

#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Aero Adventurer"
msgstr "空中冒險家"

#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Aero Adventurer"
msgstr "空中冒險家"

#. ~ Profession (male Aero Adventurer) description
#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"A budding interest in naptha and hydrocarbon powered vehicles soon blossomed"
" into a deep love of travel. With tremendous effort, you have managed to "
"make a flying aero carriage. Who knows where it shall take you?"
msgstr "對石腦油和碳氫化合物動力車輛初生的興趣很快發展成對旅行的深深熱愛。經過巨大努力，你成功製造了一輛飛行空中馬車。誰知道它會帶你去哪裡？"

#. ~ Profession (female Aero Adventurer) description
#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"A budding interest in naptha and hydrocarbon powered vehicles soon blossomed"
" into a deep love of travel. With tremendous effort, you have managed to "
"make a flying aero carriage. Who knows where it shall take you?"
msgstr "對石腦油和碳氫化合物動力車輛初生的興趣很快發展成對旅行的深深熱愛。經過巨大努力，你成功製造了一輛飛行空中馬車。誰知道它會帶你去哪裡？"

#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Steam Motorcyclist"
msgstr "蒸汽摩托車手"

#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Steam Motorcyclist"
msgstr "蒸汽摩托車手"

#. ~ Profession (male Steam Motorcyclist) description
#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"A budding interest in steam powered vehicles soon blossomed into a deep love"
" of travel. With your hands at the wheel of your trusty steam motorcycle, "
"you drive off into another adventure into the unknown."
msgstr "對蒸汽動力車輛初生的興趣很快發展成對旅行的深深熱愛。手握你信賴的蒸汽摩托車把手，你駛向未知的又一次冒險。"

#. ~ Profession (female Steam Motorcyclist) description
#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"A budding interest in steam powered vehicles soon blossomed into a deep love"
" of travel. With your hands at the wheel of your trusty steam motorcycle, "
"you drive off into another adventure into the unknown."
msgstr "對蒸汽動力車輛初生的興趣很快發展成對旅行的深深熱愛。手握你信賴的蒸汽摩托車把手，你駛向未知的又一次冒險。"

#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Town Thief"
msgstr "城鎮竊賊"

#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Town Thief"
msgstr "城鎮竊賊"

#. ~ Profession (male Town Thief) description
#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"Stealing always came easy to you, even from a young age. This talent took "
"you far in life, and now that New England has seemingly gone to the dogs, "
"you've found an entire new kind of heist."
msgstr "偷竊對你來說總是輕而易舉，甚至從年幼時就是如此。這份天賦讓你在生活中走得很遠，而現在新英格蘭似乎已陷入混亂，你發現了一種全新的盜竊方式。"

#. ~ Profession (female Town Thief) description
#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"Stealing always came easy to you, even from a young age. This talent took "
"you far in life, and now that New England has seemingly gone to the dogs, "
"you've found an entire new kind of heist."
msgstr "偷竊對你來說總是輕而易舉，甚至從年幼時就是如此。這份天賦讓你在生活中走得很遠，而現在新英格蘭似乎已陷入混亂，你發現了一種全新的盜竊方式。"

#: .\sp_terrain.json
msgid "gaslight"
msgstr "煤氣燈"

#. ~ Description for gaslight
#: .\sp_terrain.json
msgid ""
"A large lamp that combusts gas to light its surroundings.  Smashing it "
"doesn't seem like it'd produce any worthwhile salvage."
msgstr "一種通過燃燒氣體來照亮周圍的大型燈具。砸碎它似乎不會產生任何有價值的回收物。"

#: .\sp_terrain.json
msgid "SMASH!"
msgstr "砰！"

#. ~ Description for gaslight
#: .\sp_terrain.json
msgid ""
"A lamp that combusts gas to light its surroundings.  Smashing it doesn't "
"seem like it'd produce any worthwhile salvage."
msgstr "一種通過燃燒氣體來照亮周圍的燈具。砸碎它似乎不會產生任何有價值的回收物。"

#: .\sp_vehicles.json
msgid "Steam Autocarriage"
msgstr "蒸汽汽車"

#: .\sp_vehicles.json
msgid "Aero Carriage"
msgstr "空中馬車"

#: .\sp_vehicles.json
msgid "1000 KW aero turbine engine"
msgid_plural "1000 KW aero turbine engines"
msgstr[0] "1000 千瓦航空渦輪發動機"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '1000 KW aero turbine engine'}
#: .\sp_vehicles.json
msgid ""
"An aero turbine engine, usually used for military vehicles.  Known for its "
"high rate of fuel consumption. Can use a variety of fuels"
msgstr "一種航空渦輪發動機，通常用於軍用車輛。以其高燃料消耗率而聞名。可以使用多種燃料"

#: .\sp_vehicles.json
msgid "Steam Motorcycle"
msgstr "蒸汽摩托車"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid "crank machine rifle"
msgid_plural "crank machine rifles"
msgstr[0] "手搖機槍"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid ""
"This is a compact hand-cycled gun capable of firing through paper cartidges "
"with a rapidity once only seen in crew-served gatling guns!"
msgstr "這是一種緊湊的手搖槍，能夠快速發射紙質彈殼，其速度曾僅見於多人操作的加特林機槍！"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid "semi-auto"
msgstr "半自動"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid "auto"
msgstr "自動"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid "plunkett's long range pistol"
msgid_plural "plunkett's long range pistols"
msgstr[0] "普倫基特長程手槍"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid ""
"A beautifully decorated pistol.  Developed specifally for usage at long "
"ranges beyond the range where most black powder pistols are useful."
msgstr "一把裝飾精美的手槍。專為遠距離使用而設計，射程超越大多數黑火藥手槍的有效範圍。"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid "Mk.I High Velocity Pistol"
msgid_plural "Mk.I High Velocity Pistols"
msgstr[0] "Mk.I高速手槍"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid ""
"A somewhat ugly, but entirely serviceable pistol.  Developed specifally for "
"acclerating cartridge shot to a high velocity, thus increasing the lethality"
" of the pistol."
msgstr "一把略顯醜陋但完全實用的手槍。專為將彈殼加速至高速而設計，從而提升手槍的殺傷力。"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid "Springfield Hand Cannon"
msgid_plural "Springfield Hand Cannons"
msgstr[0] "斯普林菲爾德手持火炮"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid ""
"An ornately-made and very large pistol.  Fires high-bore rounds made "
"specifically for usage in rare firearms, this pistol's power is nearly "
"unmatched."
msgstr "一把裝飾華麗且體積巨大的手槍。發射專為稀有火器設計的大口徑彈藥，其威力幾乎無與倫比。"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid "Armstrong rifled Cannon"
msgid_plural "Armstrong rifled Cannons"
msgstr[0] "阿姆斯特朗線膛炮"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid ""
"An ferocious firearm capable of firing high-bore ammunition. This rifle's "
"power is nearly unmatched."
msgstr "一種兇猛的火器，能夠發射大口徑彈藥。這把步槍的威力幾乎無與倫比。"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid "westinghouse electricity projector"
msgid_plural "westinghouse electricity projectors"
msgstr[0] "西屋電氣投射器"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid ""
"A powerful electricity projector developed by the famed inventor \"C.H. "
"Westinghouse\".  Especially effective against electronic targets."
msgstr "由著名發明家“C.H. Westinghouse”開發的強大電氣投射器。對電子目標尤其有效。"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid "Zalinski pyrotechnic gun"
msgid_plural "Zalinski pyrotechnic guns"
msgstr[0] "扎林斯基煙火槍"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid ""
"A compound gun that uses a small charge of fuel to superheat lead shot to "
"near-incandescent temperatures. Does damage mainly via extreme heating of "
"the target."
msgstr "一種複合槍，使用少量燃料將鉛彈加熱至接近白熾溫度。主要通過極端加熱目標造成傷害。"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid "Foch's Warbringer"
msgid_plural "Foch's Warbringer"
msgstr[0] "福煦的戰神使者"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid ""
"A very powerful five-round revolver.  Crafted by the powerful artisans of "
"years long past, this weapon is exceedingly rare and hard to replicate."
msgstr "一把非常強大的五發左輪手槍。由久遠年代的強大工匠打造，此武器極其稀有且難以複製。"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid "shocking staff"
msgid_plural "shocking staffs"
msgstr[0] "電擊法杖"

#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'shocking staff'}.
#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'shocking staff (active)'}.
#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid "Activate"
msgstr "激活"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'shocking staff'}.
#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid "Staff starts to crackle with energy provided by current!"
msgstr "法杖開始因電流提供的能量而噼啪作響！"

#. ~ Use action need_charges_msg for {'str': 'shocking staff'}.
#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid "The staff remains the same. It needs more energy to function."
msgstr "法杖保持不變。它需要更多能量才能運作。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'shocking staff'}
#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid ""
"A steel staff with an array of electrodes on its offensive end.  Activate to"
" produce a current on the weapon, running off of batteries."
msgstr "一根鋼製法杖，攻擊端裝有一組電極。激活後可在武器上產生電流，由電池供電。"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid "shocking staff (active)"
msgid_plural "shocking staff (active)s"
msgstr[0] "電擊法杖（激活）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'shocking staff (active)'}.
#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid "Current disappears from the staff."
msgstr "電流從法杖上消失。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'shocking staff (active)'}
#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid ""
"A steel staff with an array of electrodes on its offensive end.  The staff "
"currently crackles with energy, running off of batteries."
msgstr "一根鋼製法杖，攻擊端裝有一組電極。法杖目前因能量而噼啪作響，由電池供電。"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid "Paterson mechanized gun"
msgid_plural "Paterson mechanized guns"
msgstr[0] "帕特森機械化槍"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid ""
"This is a compact recoil-cycled gun capable of firing through paper "
"cartidges with a rapidity equivalent to that of five soldiers!"
msgstr "這是一把緊湊的後坐力循環槍，能夠快速發射紙質彈殼，其射速相當於五名士兵！"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid "3 rd."
msgstr "3 發"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid "Faraday staff"
msgid_plural "Faraday staffs"
msgstr[0] "法拉第法杖"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid ""
"An upgraded version of the shocking staff, allows one to fire bolts of "
"electricity directly."
msgstr "電擊法杖的升級版本，允許直接發射電擊束。"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid "westinghouse charged accelerator"
msgid_plural "westinghouse charged accelerators"
msgstr[0] "西屋充能加速器"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid ""
"A powerful charged accelerator developed by the famed inventor \"C.H. "
"Westinghouse\".  Uses a magnetic accelerator to propel minute charges to a "
"very, very high velocity. Kill your enemies with a jolt of lightning!"
msgstr "由著名發明家“C.H. Westinghouse”開發的強大充能加速器。使用磁力加速器將微小電荷推進至極高速度。用一道閃電擊殺你的敵人！"

#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid "spring spear"
msgid_plural "spring spears"
msgstr[0] "彈簧矛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'spring spear'}
#: .\sp_weapon.json
msgid "A stout wooden pole with a spring-tensioned metal spearhead."
msgstr "一根堅固的木杆，配有彈簧張力的金屬矛頭。"

#: .\startlocation.json .\map\steam_town\overmap_terrain.json
msgid "local town"
msgstr "當地小鎮"

#: .\map\automaton_base\overmap_terrain.json
msgid "scientist compound"
msgstr "科學家化合物"

#: .\map\automaton_base\overmap_terrain.json
msgid "scientist compound roof"
msgstr "科學家園區屋頂"

#: .\map\crimhouse\overmap_terrain.json
msgid "Shady Warehouse"
msgstr "陰暗倉庫"

#: .\map\crimhouse\overmap_terrain.json
msgid "Shady Warehouse roof"
msgstr "陰暗倉庫屋頂"

#: .\map\steam_town\overmap_terrain.json
msgid "local town roof"
msgstr "本地小鎮屋頂"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Steampunk Mod Locator Hologram"
msgstr "蒸汽朋克模組定位器全息影像"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Hologram Protection"
msgstr "全息影像防護"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Hologram Protection'}
#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "\"I am programmed to not engage wandering monsters.\""
msgstr "\"我的程序設定為不與遊蕩怪物交戰。\""

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Steampunk Mod Scientist Compound Locator Hologram"
msgstr "蒸汽朋克模組科學家園區定位器全息影像"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Steampunk Mod Shady Warehouse Locator Hologram"
msgstr "蒸汽朋克模組陰暗倉庫定位器全息影像"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Go to Scientist Compound'}'
#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Go to Scientist Compound"
msgstr "前往科學家園區"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"You want me to find this location for you to explore? Sure, you will just "
"need to wait for a couple of minutes or less for me to find it via my "
"network system"
msgstr "要我為你定位探索地點？沒問題，只需等我用網絡系統查找幾分鐘或更短時間"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"You want me to locate it now for you to explore? Sure, just tell me, you "
"will just need to wait for a couple of minutes or less for me to find it via"
" my network system"
msgstr "你想讓我現在為你定位那個地點以便探索嗎？當然，告訴我吧，你只需要等幾分鐘或更短時間，我就能通過網絡系統找到它。"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Good luck to you!"
msgstr "祝你好運！"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"Not interested in explorations of new locations? No rush hopefully. You can "
"come back to me later. I'm sure that you will. Because I believe that you "
"are not a boring person"
msgstr "對新地點的探索不感興趣嗎？別急，希望如此。你可以稍後再來找我。我相信你會的，因為我覺得你不是個無聊的人。"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Use your wits for your own safety hopefully as well"
msgstr "也希望你運用智慧確保自身安全。"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Have you went to this location that I have found for you to explore?"
msgstr "你去過我為你找到的那個探索地點了嗎？"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Good work!"
msgstr "幹得好！"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"What's the point of lying to me? You think I'm gonna reward you? Your "
"rewards for this mission is valuable for you items or living creatures or "
"other survivors you manage to find in this location which I have found for "
"you to explore"
msgstr ""
"對我撒謊有什麼意義？你以為我會獎勵你嗎？這次任務的獎勵就是你在那個地點找到的對你來說有價值的物品、生物或其他倖存者，那是我為你找到的探索地點。"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"You are a boring, lazy person honestly. I guess that laziness applies to "
"both of us"
msgstr "說實話，你是個無聊又懶惰的人。我想懶惰這一點我們倆都適用。"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Go to Shady Warehouse'}'
#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Go to Shady Warehouse"
msgstr "前往陰暗倉庫"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"System is online. Initiate conversation mode. Look at that. Survivor has "
"managed to activate a hologram projector easily! Yeah, my creators know many"
" types of you who don't even read what's written on items honestly. Good "
"that you seem like a pretty intelligent person hopefully. So, do you want me"
" to show you where this location is via my network system? I can grant you "
"access to archived global network system which my creators have managed to "
"restore. However, after usage I will need to recharge a little bit which "
"only means that you will need to wait to use this function again hopefully"
msgstr ""
"系統在線。啟動對話模式。看啊，倖存者輕鬆激活了全息投影儀！沒錯，我的創造者瞭解很多像你這樣的人，說實話他們甚至不讀物品上的說明。幸好你看起來是個相當聰明的人，希望如此。那麼，你想讓我通過網絡系統為你顯示這個地點的位置嗎？我可以授予你訪問存檔全球網絡系統的權限，那是我的創造者設法恢復的。不過，使用後我需要稍微充能，這意味著你需要等待才能再次使用這個功能，希望如此。"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"[MISSIONS] I want you to find this location for me to explore it hopefully "
"via your network system"
msgstr "[任務] 我希望你通過你的網絡系統為我找到這個地點以便探索，希望如此。"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Who or what are you?"
msgstr "你是誰或是什麼東西？"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"Who are your creators? What is the purpose of producing these projectors?"
msgstr "你的創造者是誰？製造這些投影儀的目的是什麼？"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"[IMPROVE MOOD] I want you to grant me access to archived global network "
"system"
msgstr "[改善心情] 我希望你授予我訪問存檔全球網絡系統的權限。"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "About that mission..."
msgstr "關於那個任務……"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "[GOODBYE]"
msgstr "[告別]"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"Initiate search mode. Please, wait for a couple of minutes or less. You've "
"heard me clearly. Still, we have limitations with regards to our locating "
"tools. If locator does not manage to find this location then simply create "
"another hologram locator of which can find this location successfully"
msgstr ""
"啟動搜索模式。請等待幾分鐘或更短時間。你聽清楚了。不過，我們的定位工具有所限制。如果定位器無法找到這個地點，那就簡單地創建另一個能成功找到該地點的全息定位器。"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Can I talk to you about something else?"
msgstr "我能和你談談別的嗎？"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Thanks"
msgstr "謝謝。"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"I'm a magic genie from a magic camera. No, I'm just joking. What kind of a "
"question is this? You don't like to explore or don't know much about your "
"own world? Have not you seen stuff in labs? Military structures? Top secret "
"stuff? Aliens or whatever these creatures are? You think that your own "
"people don't have tech which can produce holograms? I'm a hologram, software"
" with some additional technologies, it is that simple"
msgstr ""
"我是魔法相機裡的魔法精靈。不，開個玩笑。這是什麼問題？你不喜歡探索，還是對自己的世界瞭解不多？你沒在實驗室裡見過東西嗎？軍事設施？絕密物品？外星人或那些生物？你以為你們自己人沒有能製造全息影像的技術嗎？我是個全息影像，是帶有附加技術的軟件，就這麼簡單。"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"This question is much more intelligent than the other one. My creators can "
"be described as a bunch of highly technological geeks majority of which are "
"humans honestly. They neither possess that many combat skills nor they are "
"that interested in subjecting their lives to unnecessary risk clearly. They "
"only engage hostile creatures for basic survival needs. They try to rely on "
"self-sufficiency with relative success thanks to their applied intelligence "
"along with tech that they have managed to find or engineer themselves. They "
"have made these projectors so that we can help each other. We provide you "
"with locations with dangerous creatures along with valuable items or "
"survivors who are captive. You clear these locations acquiring whatever "
"valuable items or survivors you want from there making these locations safe "
"shelters where we including you can live hopefully as well"
msgstr ""
"這個問題比上一個聰明多了。我的創造者可以說是一群高科技極客，說實話其中大多數是人類。他們既沒有太多戰鬥技能，也顯然不願讓自己的生命承受不必要的風險。他們只會在基本生存需要時與敵對生物交戰。他們試圖依靠自給自足，並憑藉應用智慧和自行發現或設計的技術取得相對成功。他們製造這些投影儀是為了我們能互相幫助。我們為你提供有危險生物的地點，以及有價值的物品或被囚禁的倖存者。你清理這些地點，從中獲取你想要的任何有價值物品或倖存者，使這些地點成為安全的庇護所，希望我們包括你也能在那裡生活。"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"What do you want to do? Play archived games? Browse archived social media? "
"Watch archived videos? Listen to archived music? Read archived files along "
"with archived books? Something to play, read, listen, watch for fun, "
"intelligence improving, spiritual improving, mental improving?"
msgstr ""
"你想做什麼？玩存檔遊戲？瀏覽存檔社交媒體？看存檔視頻？聽存檔音樂？閱讀存檔文件和存檔書籍？找點東西玩、讀、聽、看，為了樂趣、提升智力、精神提升、心智改善？"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "I like some of these a lot honestly. Healthy stuff"
msgstr "說實話，我很喜歡其中一些。健康的東西。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_sp_town_guardnpc.json
msgid "Hello, Madam."
msgstr "您好，夫人。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_sp_town_guardnpc.json
msgid "Hello, Sir."
msgstr "您好，先生。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_sp_town_guardnpc.json
msgid "Thank you, Do you know where I am?"
msgstr "謝謝，您知道我現在身處何處嗎？"

#: .\npcs\Talk_sp_town_guardnpc.json
msgid ""
"You've stumbled upon our little town, a bit of an oasis in these troubled "
"times, if I do say so myself! Make yourself at home, but don't overstay your"
" welcome."
msgstr "您偶然發現了我們的小鎮，要我說，在這動盪時期，這裡可算是一片綠洲！請隨意安頓，但別逗留太久。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_sp_town_guardnpc.json
msgid "Got it. Thanks."
msgstr "明白了，謝謝。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_sp_town_guardnpc.json
msgid "I shall return."
msgstr "我會回來的。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_sp_town_mannpc.json
msgid ""
"Welcome, dear madam, to our little village. Please make yourself "
"comfortable, I think a woman of your stature is safer here than in the "
"outside world."
msgstr "歡迎，親愛的夫人，來到我們的小村莊。請隨意安頓，我認為像您這樣地位的女士在這裡比在外界更安全。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_sp_town_mannpc.json
msgid ""
"Another wayfarer has found our oasis in the abyss of violence that surrounds"
" us! Good sir, I think you'll have a fine time here, plenty of friendly men "
"and women. Although sometimes the women can be a little too friendly, if you"
" ask me!"
msgstr ""
"又一位旅人發現了我們這片暴力深淵中的綠洲！好先生，我想您在這裡會過得愉快，有許多友善的男男女女。不過，要我說，有時候女士們可能有點過於熱情了！"

#: .\npcs\Talk_sp_town_mannpc.json
msgid ""
"So you're a man in this town? What does someone of your status do in these "
"parts?"
msgstr "那麼您是這鎮上的男人？像您這樣身份的人在這裡都做些什麼？"

#: .\npcs\Talk_sp_town_mannpc.json .\npcs\Talk_sp_town_womnpc.json
#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json .\npcs\sp_merchants.json
msgid "Goodbye, thank you for your time."
msgstr "再見，謝謝你的時間。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_sp_town_mannpc.json
msgid ""
"A woman like you should get the grasp of it, I act as the head of my "
"household, work in the mill, and defend the town in times of trouble. Sure, "
"it might not be fit for a woman, but what more could a man ask for in this "
"life?"
msgstr "像您這樣的女士應該能理解，我作為一家之主，在磨坊工作，並在危難時刻保衛小鎮。當然，這可能不適合女性，但一個男人這輩子還能要求什麼呢？"

#: .\npcs\Talk_sp_town_mannpc.json
msgid ""
"A fellow gentleman like you should understand well enough, I act as the head"
" of my household, work in the mill, and defend the town in times of trouble."
" What more could a man ask for in this life?"
msgstr "像您這樣的紳士應該很明白，我作為一家之主，在磨坊工作，並在危難時刻保衛小鎮。一個男人這輩子還能要求什麼呢？"

#: .\npcs\Talk_sp_town_mannpc.json .\npcs\Talk_sp_town_womnpc.json
#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json .\npcs\sp_merchants.json
msgid "Got it."
msgstr "明白了。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_sp_town_womnpc.json
msgid ""
"Ah, I see another fine woman has come to visit our community. Please, do "
"make yourself comfortable. We're very welcoming around here."
msgstr "啊，看來又有一位優雅的女士來拜訪我們的社區了。請務必隨意安頓。我們這裡非常熱情好客。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_sp_town_womnpc.json
msgid ""
"Hello, fine gentleman, to our humble town. This is a quite a nice town, is "
"it not? Perhaps a fine place to settle down in during these troubled times.."
msgstr "您好，優雅的先生，歡迎來到我們簡陋的小鎮。這是個相當不錯的小鎮，不是嗎？或許是在這動盪時期安頓下來的好地方。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_sp_town_womnpc.json
msgid "So you're a woman in this town? What do you do around here?"
msgstr "那麼您是這鎮上的女人？您在這裡都做些什麼？"

#: .\npcs\Talk_sp_town_womnpc.json
msgid ""
"Oh the usual: cooking, cleaning, gardening and so on. It seems tedious at "
"first, but you eventually get used to it. Seeing as how you're a woman, too,"
" I imagine you have the same understanding."
msgstr "哦，就是平常那些：做飯、打掃、園藝等等。起初可能覺得乏味，但最終會習慣的。既然您也是女性，我想您有同樣的理解。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_sp_town_womnpc.json
msgid ""
"Oh the usual: cooking, cleaning, gardening and so on. It seems tedious at "
"first, but you eventually get used to it. You're a man though, so I imagine "
"you're more suited to the more authoritative parts of life."
msgstr "哦，就是平常那些：做飯、打掃、園藝等等。起初可能覺得乏味，但最終會習慣的。不過您是男人，所以我想您更適合生活中那些更有權威的部分。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json .\npcs\sp_merchants.json
msgid ""
"Hello, Sir. Do you perhaps have any interest in my wares? A firearm or tonic"
" for your health perhaps?"
msgstr "您好，先生。您或許對我的商品感興趣？來把槍械或健康藥水如何？"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json .\npcs\sp_merchants.json
msgid ""
"Hello, Madam. Do you perhaps have any interests in my wares? Perhaps a nice "
"dress or some cookware to help you in your domestic pursuits."
msgstr "您好，夫人。您或許對我的商品感興趣？也許是一件漂亮的連衣裙或一些廚具，以助您操持家務。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json .\npcs\sp_merchants.json
msgid "So you're a merchant in this town? What can you tell me about it?"
msgstr "那麼您是這鎮上的商人？您能告訴我些什麼？"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json .\npcs\sp_merchants.json
msgid "Let me browse your wares."
msgstr "讓我看看您的商品。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json .\npcs\sp_merchants.json
msgid ""
"That's a good question, sir. This town has been around for some time, I "
"don't really remember how long, but we first placed roots down here in the "
"19th century. This is a place where an enterprising man such as yourself "
"could become famous."
msgstr ""
"這是個好問題，先生。這個小鎮已經存在一段時間了，我不太記得具體多久，但我們最初在19世紀就在這裡紮根了。這是一個像您這樣有進取心的人可以成名的地方。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json .\npcs\sp_merchants.json
msgid ""
"That's a good question, miss. This town has been around for some time, I "
"don't really remember how long, but we first placed roots down here in the "
"19th century. There's a lot of fine domestic pursuits here for a member of "
"the fairer sex such as yourself."
msgstr ""
"問得好，小姐。這座城鎮已經存在一段時間了，我不太記得具體多久，但我們在19世紀首次在此紮根。對於像您這樣的淑女來說，這裡有許多優雅的居家消遣。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid "Retrieve three mechanics related books"
msgstr "取回三本機械相關書籍"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Retrieve three mechanics related
#. books'}'
#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid ""
"Retrieve three copies of the guide on Mechanical Knowledge the Steamtown "
"Merchant."
msgstr "取回三份《機械知識指南》交給蒸汽鎮商人。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid ""
"I need you to prove your worth to me first. Find three copies of the Guide "
"on Mechanical Knowledge, then I might trust you some more."
msgstr "我需要你先向我證明你的價值。找到三份《機械知識指南》，然後我或許會更信任你一些。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid ""
"The Guide on Mechanical Knowledge is the absolute foundation of our network "
"of towns. Without it, we would still be woefully primitive. Get me three "
"copies of it."
msgstr "《機械知識指南》是我們城鎮網絡的絕對基石。沒有它，我們仍將處於可悲的原始狀態。給我找來三份。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid "Great news, now go out and find some for me, okay?"
msgstr "好消息，現在出去幫我找一些來，好嗎？"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid "Why ask about a task and then reject it?"
msgstr "為什麼問了任務又拒絕？"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid ""
"Look around at a shady warehouse or a scientist compound for them. Beware of"
" the thugs and automatons that hang out around those parts, though."
msgstr "去那些陰暗的倉庫或科學家據點附近找找看。不過要小心那些地方遊蕩的暴徒和自動機械。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid "Have you found the books yet?"
msgstr "你找到那些書了嗎？"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid "Superlative work, I might have more tasks for you in the future"
msgstr "幹得漂亮，將來我可能還有更多任務交給你。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid "That's odd, I don't really know what to say."
msgstr "真奇怪，我都不知道該說什麼了。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid ""
"Oh well, at least you tried. That's more than what most people do around "
"here."
msgstr "唉，至少你嘗試過了。這比這裡大多數人做的都要多。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid "Kill the gangsters"
msgstr "消滅幫派分子"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid ""
"You seem to know a lot about the area around our little town, but the thugs "
"do as well"
msgstr "你似乎對我們小鎮周邊地區很瞭解，但那些暴徒也一樣。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid ""
"You seem to have no small amount of grit and determination. How about this, "
"you go out and kill a few criminals that have been plaguing us as of late. "
"About seven should suffice."
msgstr "你似乎頗有膽識和決心。這樣如何，你出去幹掉幾個最近一直困擾我們的罪犯。大約七個就夠了。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid ""
"Thank you for accepting, you'll be reimbursed handsomely if you kill those "
"ruffians for us."
msgstr "感謝你接受，如果你為我們除掉那些惡棍，你會得到豐厚的報酬。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid ""
"It's shame that you would reject my offer, but I understand the risk. "
"Getting stabbed to death by some criminal's shiv isn't a very tempting "
"propect!"
msgstr "你拒絕我的提議真是遺憾，但我理解其中的風險。被某個罪犯的刀捅死可不是什麼誘人的前景！"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid ""
"The criminals hide out at shady warehouses, and shady warehouses alone."
msgstr "罪犯們藏匿在陰暗的倉庫裡，而且只在那裡。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid "Have the ruffians been dispatched yet?"
msgstr "那些惡棍已經被解決了嗎？"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid ""
"Astounding work! Our town will be a little bit safer now, as will all of New"
" England."
msgstr "幹得驚人！現在我們的城鎮會安全一點，整個新英格蘭地區也會如此。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid "I'm not entirely sure if you're telling the truth, but alright."
msgstr "我不完全確定你說的是真話，但好吧。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid "So you've decided to give up already?"
msgstr "所以你已經決定放棄了？"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid "Kill Mad Scientist"
msgstr "消滅瘋狂科學家"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid ""
"You've done more than enough to gain our trust, but I have another task for "
"you."
msgstr "你已經做得足夠多，贏得了我們的信任，但我還有另一個任務給你。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid ""
"There are these people that have been causing massive problems recently. "
"People of eccentric natures, poisoned with an awful intelligence. Them and "
"their handiwork have terrorized our communities for a long while, and I "
"think you should handle it what do you think?"
msgstr ""
"最近有一些人造成了巨大的問題。這些人性格古怪，被一種可怕的智慧所毒害。他們和他們的作品長期以來一直恐嚇著我們的社區，我認為你應該處理一下，你覺得呢？"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid ""
"I appreciate your willingness to go after these wayward scientist, but do be"
" careful."
msgstr "我很感激你願意去追捕這些誤入歧途的科學家，但一定要小心。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid "While I am disheartened by your reply, I understand entirely."
msgstr "雖然你的回答讓我感到失望，但我完全理解。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid ""
"Mad scientists can be found in the scientist compounds that dot the "
"landscape. Be careful, as they are very skilled with electricity and the "
"creation of automatons."
msgstr "瘋狂科學家可以在遍佈各地的科學家據點中找到。小心點，因為他們非常擅長電學和製造自動機械。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid "Are they dead yet?"
msgstr "他們死了嗎？"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid ""
"To be honest, I didn't think you would make it back alive. Here is a reward "
"for your immense efforts."
msgstr "說實話，我沒想到你能活著回來。這是對你巨大努力的獎勵。"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid ""
"Are you sure you're telling the truth about these scientists you have "
"killed?"
msgstr "你確定你關於這些被你殺死的科學家說的是真話嗎？"

#: .\npcs\Talk_steamtown_merchant.json
msgid "What a shame, but I guess you weren't as strong as we expected."
msgstr "真遺憾，但我想你並沒有我們預期的那麼強大。"

#: .\npcs\sp_factions.json
msgid "Secluded Towns"
msgstr "隱秘城鎮"

#. ~ Description for Secluded Towns
#: .\npcs\sp_factions.json
msgid ""
"A collection of small industrial towns that dot the landscape. Curiously "
"retrogade and retrofuturist in many of their characterstics."
msgstr "一片散佈在景觀中的小型工業城鎮群。其許多特徵奇異地呈現出復古與復古未來主義的風格。"

#: .\npcs\sp_merchants.json
msgid "Steam Merchant"
msgstr "蒸汽商人"

#: .\npcs\sp_merchants.json .\npcs\sp_npc_classes.json
msgid "I'm a local shopkeeper."
msgstr "我是本地店主。"

#: .\npcs\sp_merchants.json
msgid "Do you have a task for me?"
msgstr "你有任務給我嗎？"

#: .\npcs\sp_npc_classes.json
msgid "Town Guard"
msgstr "城鎮守衛"

#: .\npcs\sp_npc_classes.json
msgid "town guard"
msgstr "城鎮守衛"

#: .\npcs\sp_npc_classes.json
msgid "Protects the town from assailants"
msgstr "保護城鎮免受襲擊者侵擾"

#: .\npcs\sp_npc_classes.json
msgid "Townswoman"
msgstr "城鎮婦女"

#: .\npcs\sp_npc_classes.json
msgid "townswoman"
msgstr "城鎮婦女"

#: .\npcs\sp_npc_classes.json
msgid "A woman who lives in a local town"
msgstr "一位居住在本地城鎮的女性"

#: .\npcs\sp_npc_classes.json
msgid "Townsman"
msgstr "城鎮男子"

#: .\npcs\sp_npc_classes.json
msgid "townsman"
msgstr "城鎮男子"

#: .\npcs\sp_npc_classes.json
msgid "A man who lives in a local town"
msgstr "一位居住在本地城鎮的男性"

#: .\npcs\sp_npc_classes.json
msgid "Steamtown Merchant"
msgstr "蒸汽鎮商人"
